Class SAML2Proxy

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.openam.authentication.modules.saml2.SAML2Proxy

  • public final class SAML2Proxy
extends Object
    Called on the way back into the SAML2 Authentication Module by the saml2AuthAssertionConsumer jsp.
